    m_Localized: "\u2692\uFE0F MATERIAL"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25083740373221382
    m_Localized: "\u2726 ET\xC9REO"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25083740373221383
    m_Localized: CONFIRMAR OFRENDA
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25083740373221384
    m_Localized: "Tu camino est\xE1 sellado. Bienvenido."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25083740377415680
    m_Localized: ASPIRANTE
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25083740377415681
    m_Localized: MAESTRO
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25083740377415682
    m_Localized: "OR\xC1CULO"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25083740377415683
    m_Localized: "Las L\xEDneas Ley est\xE1n alineadas."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25083740377415684
    m_Localized: "El \xE9ter est\xE1 turbulento aqu\xED. Prueba en otro lugar."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25083740377415685
    m_Localized: Esperando el aliento sagrado...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25083740377415686
    m_Localized: Comenzando el Ritual del Rostro.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25083740377415687
    m_Localized: El camino de la sombra revela tu verdadera esencia.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25083740377415688
    m_Localized: Reino Desconocido
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25083740377415689
    m_Localized: "Tu legado a\xFAn no se ha escrito..."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25083740377415690
    m_Localized: MANIFESTO
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25083740381609984
    m_Localized: "INTENCI\xD3N"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25083740381609985
    m_Localized: "BR\xDAJULA"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25083740381609986
    m_Localized: "MEDITA CON EL OR\xC1CULO"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25083740381609987
    m_Localized: Describe tus habilidades...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25083740381609988
    m_Localized: Elige tu estilo de resonancia
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25083740381609989
    m_Localized: Persona actualizada.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25083740381609990
    m_Localized: "M\xCDSTICO"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25083740381609991
    m_Localized: NEGOCIOS
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25083740381609992
    m_Localized: CASUAL
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25083740381609993
    m_Localized: TECH
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25083740381609994
    m_Localized: SELLAR EL RITUAL
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25083740381609995
    m_Localized: CONFIRMAR DATOS
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25083740381609996
    m_Localized: GUARDAR PERFIL
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25083740381609997
    m_Localized: "\xA1VAMOS!"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25083740381609998
    m_Localized: "CONSULTAR AL OR\xC1CULO"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25083740381609999
    m_Localized: "Perfil sincronizado. El Nexus est\xE1 optimizado para su presencia."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25083740381610000
    m_Localized: Por favor, especifique su edad.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25083740381610001
    m_Localized: "Seleccione su identidad de g\xE9nero."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25083740381610002
    m_Localized: Establezca su zona operativa.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25083740381610003
    m_Localized: "\xBFCu\xE1ntos a\xF1os llevas d\xE1ndolo todo en este planeta?"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25083740381610004
    m_Localized: "\xA1Boom! Tu Aura est\xE1 lista para brillar. \xA1Nos vemos en
      el Nexus!"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
